{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":699,"text":"Why do we think"},{"time":2603,"text":"that stories by men are deemed\nto be of universal importance,"},{"time":7918,"text":"and stories by women are thought\nto be merely about women?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":14813,"text":"My grandmother left school\nwhen she was 12."},{"time":17576,"text":"She had 14 children."},{"time":20356,"text":"My mother left school when she was 15."},{"time":22271,"text":"She was a secretary."},{"time":23696,"text":"I graduated from university\nto become a theater director,"},{"time":27478,"text":"and that progress is entirely to do\nwith the fact that people I'll never meet"},{"time":31661,"text":"fought for women to have rights,"},{"time":33933,"text":"get the vote, get education,\nhave progress."},{"time":37098,"text":"And I'm determined to do the same,\nand obviously you are, too."},{"time":40707,"text":"Why not?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":41908,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":43489,"text":"So I started a festival called WOW,\nWomen of the World, seven years ago,"},{"time":47225,"text":"and it's now in 20 countries\nacross five continents."},{"time":50253,"text":"And one of those countries\nis Somaliland in Africa."},{"time":53628,"text":"So I traveled there last year,"},{"time":55867,"text":"and part of the joy I had in going there\nwas going to these caves."},{"time":62722,"text":"The Laas Geel caves."},{"time":64922,"text":"Now, these caves contain some\nof the oldest cave paintings in the world."},{"time":70999,"text":"These paintings are thought to be\nround about 9,000 to 11,000 years old."},{"time":77110,"text":"Art:"},{"time":78563,"text":"what humanity has done\never since it evolved."},{"time":82350,"text":"It's how we speak about ourselves,"},{"time":84497,"text":"how we understand our identity,"},{"time":86458,"text":"how we look at our surroundings,"},{"time":88230,"text":"who we find out about each other"},{"time":91325,"text":"because of the meaning of our lives."},{"time":93559,"text":"That's what art is for."}]},{"cues":[{"time":95971,"text":"So look at this little picture."},{"time":97957,"text":"I think it's a little girl."},{"time":99927,"text":"I thought it was a bit like me\nwhen I was a little girl."},{"time":103195,"text":"And I thought, well, who painted\nthis joyful, youthful figure?"},{"time":107386,"text":"And I asked the curator of the caves."},{"time":109514,"text":"I said, \"Tell me about the men\nand women who painted these.\""},{"time":113056,"text":"And he looked at me\nabsolutely askance, and he said,"},{"time":116557,"text":"\"Women didn't paint these pictures.\""},{"time":119241,"text":"And I said, \"Well,\nit was 11,000 years ago.\""},{"time":121769,"text":"I said, \"How do you know?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":123252,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":125803,"text":"And he said, \"Women don't do these things."},{"time":129558,"text":"Men made these marks. Women don't.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":134547,"text":"Now, I wasn't really surprised,"},{"time":138341,"text":"because that's an attitude\nthat I've seen continuously"},{"time":142423,"text":"all my life as a theater maker."},{"time":146552,"text":"We are told that divine knowledge\ncomes down through the masculine,"},{"time":152386,"text":"whether it be to the imam,\nthe priest, the rabbi, the holy man."},{"time":157421,"text":"Similarly, we're told that creative genius\nresides in the masculine,"},{"time":162741,"text":"that it is the masculine"},{"time":164511,"text":"that will be able to tell us\nabout who we really are,"},{"time":167600,"text":"that the masculine will tell\nthe universal story"},{"time":170691,"text":"on behalf of all of us,"},{"time":172602,"text":"whereas women artists will really\njust talk about women's experiences,"},{"time":177201,"text":"women's issues\nonly really relevant to women"},{"time":180601,"text":"and of passing interest to men --"},{"time":183603,"text":"and really only some men."},{"time":185909,"text":"And it's that conviction,"},{"time":188204,"text":"that that we are taught,"},{"time":189609,"text":"that I think colors so much\nof whether we're prepared to believe"},{"time":193433,"text":"that women's stories really matter."},{"time":195958,"text":"And unless we're prepared to believe\nthat women's stories really matter,"},{"time":199529,"text":"then women's rights don't really matter,"},{"time":202543,"text":"and then change can't really come."}]},{"cues":[{"time":206876,"text":"I want to tell you\nabout two examples of stories"},{"time":211610,"text":"that are thought to be\nof universal importance:"},{"time":214572,"text":"\"E.T.\" and \"Hamlet.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":217352,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":220487,"text":"So I took my two children\nwhen they were little --"},{"time":223777,"text":"Caroline was eight and Robby was five --"},{"time":227051,"text":"to see \"E.T.\""},{"time":228642,"text":"And it's a fantastic story\nof this little alien"},{"time":232051,"text":"who ends up in an American family"},{"time":234026,"text":"with a mum, two brothers and a sister,"},{"time":237259,"text":"but he wants to go home."},{"time":239720,"text":"Not only that, but some\nreally bad scientists"},{"time":242364,"text":"want to do some experiments on him,"},{"time":244762,"text":"and they're looking for him."},{"time":246993,"text":"So the children have a plot."},{"time":249073,"text":"They decide they're going to take him\nback to his spaceship"},{"time":251934,"text":"as soon as they can,"},{"time":253109,"text":"and they plop him in a bicycle basket,"},{"time":255007,"text":"and off they ride."},{"time":256373,"text":"But unfortunately, the baddies\nhave found out, and they're catching up"},{"time":260293,"text":"and they've got sirens\nand they've got their guns,"},{"time":262674,"text":"they've got the loud-hailers,\nit's terribly frightening,"},{"time":265372,"text":"and they're closing up on the children,"},{"time":267316,"text":"and the children are never\ngoing to make it."},{"time":269436,"text":"And then all of a sudden, magically,\nthe bikes fly up in the air,"},{"time":273553,"text":"over the clouds,"},{"time":275116,"text":"over the moon,"},{"time":276328,"text":"and they're going to save \"E.T.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":279394,"text":"So I turn to see my children's faces,"},{"time":281696,"text":"and Robby is enraptured,\nhe's there with them, he's saving E.T.,"},{"time":286190,"text":"he's a happy boy."},{"time":288070,"text":"And I turn to Caroline,\nand she's crying her eyes out."},{"time":291866,"text":"And I said, \"What's the matter?\""},{"time":293435,"text":"And she said, \"Why can't I save E.T.?\nWhy can't I come?\""},{"time":299422,"text":"And then all of a sudden I realized:"},{"time":301805,"text":"they weren't children;"},{"time":303857,"text":"they were boys --"},{"time":305755,"text":"all boys."},{"time":307844,"text":"And Caroline, who had invested\nso much in E.T.,"},{"time":310845,"text":"well, she wasn't invited to save him,"},{"time":313039,"text":"and she felt humiliated and spurned."}]},{"cues":[{"time":316412,"text":"So I wrote to Steven Spielberg --"}]},{"cues":[{"time":318185,"text":"(Laughter) (Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":324377,"text":"and I said, \"I don't know\nif you understand"},{"time":326951,"text":"the psychological importance\nof what's happened,"},{"time":329354,"text":"and are you prepared to pay\nfor the therapy bills?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":331878,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":333316,"text":"Twenty years later, I haven't\nhad a word back from him,"},{"time":336312,"text":"but I'm still hopeful."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337774,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":339408,"text":"But I thought it was interesting,"},{"time":341036,"text":"because if you read reviews\nof what he intended with E.T.,"},{"time":343932,"text":"he says very specifically,"},{"time":345747,"text":"\"I wanted the world to understand"},{"time":348273,"text":"that we should love\nand embrace difference.\""},{"time":351504,"text":"But somehow he didn't include\nthe idea of girls' difference"},{"time":356150,"text":"in this thinking."},{"time":357866,"text":"He thought he was writing a story\nabout all humanity."},{"time":362200,"text":"Caroline thought he was marginalizing"},{"time":364302,"text":"half of humanity."},{"time":365755,"text":"He thought he was writing a story\nabout human goodness;"},{"time":368863,"text":"she thought he was writing\na lad's heroic adventure."}]},{"cues":[{"time":374028,"text":"And this is common."},{"time":376512,"text":"Men feel they have been given the mantle\nfor universal communication,"},{"time":381657,"text":"but of course, how could they be?"},{"time":383633,"text":"They are writing from male experience\nthrough male's eyes."},{"time":390031,"text":"We have to have a look at this ourselves."},{"time":392273,"text":"We have to be prepared to go back\nthrough all our books and our films,"},{"time":395973,"text":"all our favorite things,"},{"time":397334,"text":"and say, \"Actually, this is written\nby a male artist --"},{"time":400188,"text":"not an artist."},{"time":402200,"text":"We have to see\nthat so many of these stories"},{"time":404628,"text":"are written through a male perspective."},{"time":406788,"text":"Which is fine,"},{"time":408749,"text":"but then females need to have\n50 percent of the rights"},{"time":412271,"text":"for the stage, the film, the novel,"},{"time":414849,"text":"the place of creativity."}]},{"cues":[{"time":417561,"text":"Let me talk about \"Hamlet.\""},{"time":419384,"text":"To be or not to be."},{"time":421101,"text":"That is the question."},{"time":422998,"text":"But it's not my question."},{"time":424787,"text":"My question is: Why was I taught\nas a young woman"},{"time":428560,"text":"that this was the quintessential\nexample of human dilemma"},{"time":432941,"text":"and human experience?"},{"time":434661,"text":"It's a marvelous story,"},{"time":436021,"text":"but actually, it's about a young man\nfearful that he won't be able to make it"},{"time":441381,"text":"as a powerful figure in a male world"},{"time":444070,"text":"unless he takes revenge\nfor his father's murder."},{"time":447552,"text":"He talks a great deal to us\nabout suicide being an option,"},{"time":452254,"text":"but the reality is that the person\nwho actually commits suicide, Ophelia,"},{"time":456947,"text":"after she's been humiliated\nand abused by him,"},{"time":459469,"text":"never gets a chance to talk\nto the audience about her feelings."},{"time":462669,"text":"And then when he's finished with Ophelia,\nhe turns on his mum,"},{"time":465635,"text":"because basically she has the audacity\nto fall in love with his uncle"},{"time":468958,"text":"and enjoy sex."}]},{"cues":[{"time":470194,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":472255,"text":"It is a great story,"},{"time":474367,"text":"but it is a story about male conflict,\nmale dilemma, male struggle."},{"time":480137,"text":"But I was told this was the story\nof human beings,"},{"time":484353,"text":"despite the fact that it only\nhad two women in it."},{"time":487420,"text":"And unless I reeducate myself,"},{"time":490005,"text":"I am always going to think"},{"time":491754,"text":"that women's stories\nmatter less than men's."},{"time":496166,"text":"A woman could have written \"Hamlet,\""},{"time":497925,"text":"but she would have written it differently,"},{"time":500036,"text":"and it wouldn't have had\nglobal recognition."},{"time":502668,"text":"As the writer Margaret Atwood says,"},{"time":504763,"text":"\"When a man writes about doing the dishes,"},{"time":507273,"text":"it's realism."},{"time":509379,"text":"When a woman writes about doing it,"},{"time":511524,"text":"it's an unfortunate genetic disposition.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":514063,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":515296,"text":"Now, this is not just something\nthat belongs to then."},{"time":519154,"text":"I mean, when I was a young girl,"},{"time":520978,"text":"wanting desperately\nto be a theater director,"},{"time":523626,"text":"this is what my male lecturer said to me:"},{"time":526489,"text":"\"Well, there are three women\ndirectors in Britain,\" he said, \"Jude.\""},{"time":530585,"text":"\"There's Joan Knight, who's a lesbian,\nthere's Joan Littlewood, who's retired,"},{"time":534716,"text":"and there's Buzz Goodbody,\nwho's just killed herself."},{"time":537520,"text":"So, which of those three\nwould you like to be?\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":539800,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":540877,"text":"Now, leaving aside\nthe disgusting slur on gay women,"},{"time":545487,"text":"the fact is, he wanted to humiliate me."},{"time":548356,"text":"He thought it was silly\nthat I wanted to be a director."},{"time":552139,"text":"And I told my friend Marin Alsop,\nthe conductor, and she said,"},{"time":555134,"text":"\"Oh yes, well, my music teacher\nsaid exactly the same."},{"time":557907,"text":"He said, 'Women don't conduct.'\""},{"time":560704,"text":"But all these years later,\nwe've made our mark."},{"time":563451,"text":"You think, \"Well, it'll be different now.\""},{"time":565705,"text":"I'm afraid it's not different now."},{"time":568223,"text":"The current head\nof the Paris Conservatoire"},{"time":571692,"text":"said recently, \"It takes\ngreat physical strength"},{"time":575143,"text":"to conduct a symphony,"},{"time":576648,"text":"and women are too weak.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":578123,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":579600,"text":"The artist George Baselitz said,"},{"time":581563,"text":"\"Well, the fact is women can't paint."},{"time":583874,"text":"Well -- they can't paint very well.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":586194,"text":"The writer V.S. Naipaul\nsaid two years ago,"},{"time":588606,"text":"\"I can read two paragraphs and know\nimmediately if it's written by a woman,"},{"time":592222,"text":"and I just stop reading,\nbecause it's not worthy of me.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":594947,"text":"Audience: Whoa!"}]},{"cues":[{"time":597389,"text":"And it goes on."}]},{"cues":[{"time":600997,"text":"We have to find a way"},{"time":603009,"text":"of stopping young girls and women"},{"time":605677,"text":"feeling not only that\ntheir story doesn't matter,"},{"time":608542,"text":"but they're not allowed\nto be the storyteller."},{"time":612661,"text":"Because once you feel\nthat you can't stand in the central space"},{"time":616268,"text":"and speak on behalf of the world,"},{"time":619300,"text":"you will feel that you can offer\nyour goods up to a small, select group."},{"time":624399,"text":"You will tend to do smaller work\non smaller stages,"},{"time":627939,"text":"your economic power will be less,"},{"time":629996,"text":"your reach of audiences will be less,"},{"time":632492,"text":"and your credit will be less as an artist."},{"time":637557,"text":"And we do finally give artists\nthese incredible, prominent spaces"},{"time":642836,"text":"in the world,"},{"time":644024,"text":"because they are our storytellers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":645787,"text":"Now, why should it matter to you\nif you're not an artist?"},{"time":648940,"text":"Supposing you're an accountant\nor an entrepreneur or a medic"},{"time":652209,"text":"or a scientist:"},{"time":653400,"text":"Should you care about women artists?"},{"time":656026,"text":"Absolutely, you must,"},{"time":658106,"text":"because as you can see\nfrom the cave paintings,"},{"time":661542,"text":"all civilizations,"},{"time":663247,"text":"all of humanity"},{"time":666105,"text":"have relied upon artists\nto tell the human story,"},{"time":670085,"text":"and if the human story\nis finally told by men,"},{"time":673378,"text":"take my word for it,"},{"time":675138,"text":"it will be about men."}]},{"cues":[{"time":677671,"text":"So let's make a change."},{"time":680379,"text":"Let's make a change\nto all our institutions,"},{"time":682605,"text":"and not just in the West."},{"time":683904,"text":"Don't forget -- this message\nof incapability of women"},{"time":688347,"text":"to hold creative genius"},{"time":690396,"text":"is being told to girls and women\nin Nigeria, in China, in Russia,"},{"time":695334,"text":"in Indonesia."},{"time":696521,"text":"All over the world, girls\nand women are being told"},{"time":699254,"text":"that they can't finally hold the idea\nof creative inspiration."},{"time":705131,"text":"And I want to ask you:"},{"time":706804,"text":"Do you believe that?"},{"time":708542,"text":"Do you believe that women\ncan be a creative genius?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":713168,"text":"(Applause and cheers)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":718931,"text":"Well then, please go forward,"},{"time":720616,"text":"support women artists,"},{"time":722890,"text":"buy their work,"},{"time":724388,"text":"insist that their voices are heard,"},{"time":726680,"text":"find platforms on which\ntheir voices will be made."},{"time":730680,"text":"And remember this:"},{"time":732491,"text":"that in a sense, if we're going\nto get past this moment"},{"time":735794,"text":"of a world where we know\nthat we are unequal,"},{"time":739670,"text":"it's artists who have to imagine\na different world."},{"time":742891,"text":"And I'm calling on all artists,\nwomen and men,"},{"time":746525,"text":"to imagine a gender-equal world."},{"time":750326,"text":"Let's paint it. Let's draw it."},{"time":752533,"text":"Let's write about it. Let's film it."},{"time":754352,"text":"And if we could imagine it,"},{"time":756262,"text":"then we would have the energy\nand the stamina"},{"time":759766,"text":"to work towards it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":761802,"text":"When I see this little girl,"},{"time":763880,"text":"11,000 years ago,"},{"time":765944,"text":"I want to know that the little girl now"},{"time":769429,"text":"can stand there and think\nshe's entitled to her dreams,"},{"time":772737,"text":"she's entitled to her destiny"},{"time":775051,"text":"and she's entitled to speak\non behalf of the whole world,"},{"time":779277,"text":"be recognized for it"},{"time":781125,"text":"and applauded."}]},{"cues":[{"time":782799,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":784009,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}